more about how you plan to address this feedback or what steps you've taken so far? This will help others who might be facing similar challenges."', 'As an electrician turned health enthusiast, I can relate to the frustration of putting effort into something and having it dismissed. @jolly-map, have you considered reaching out to Anita for a more detailed discussion? Sometimes, people just need a chance to explain their perspective. It could also be beneficial to document your creative process and the thought behind your work; this can serve as a powerful tool when discussing your art.', '""
